{"questionId":"11757","questionHtml":"<p>Write down two more equations for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n</math></span> and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"c\">\n  <mi>c</mi>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt to substitute either (5, 38) or (7, 24)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"25a + 5b + c = 38\">\n  <mn>25</mn>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>5</mn>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>38</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A</strong><strong>1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"49a + 7b + c = 24\">\n  <mn>49</mn>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>7</mn>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>24</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A</strong><strong>1 </strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11757","referenceCode":"EXM.2.SL.TZ0.3b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down two more equations for a , b and c .","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.6—Modelling skills"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}